{"tid":980936,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【留12吋疤】加個fb朋友無咗半個肝 醋男以為撬牆腳刀插「情敵」","createTime":"2019-01-14T00:40:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-14T06:58:30.000Z","uid":130626,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"09c9d2b4f92edea0e10f1d0b52ebecab4e6e242c","tid":980936,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T00:40:51.000Z","msg":"英國有男子不滿陌生男在facebook向女友傳交友邀請，心生妒恨繼而用刀襲擊對方，令其胸口留下12吋疤痕並失去半個肝臟。法官認為此舉是明顯單純的接觸，被告施襲令人震驚，判他入獄7年。<br />\n26歲的亨特（Ross Hunter）被控於上年10月，在巴士站持廚刀襲擊霍根（Aaron Hogan）。霍根胸口被刺後慌忙逃命，要負傷攀過6呎高的大閘才避開亨特襲擊，他傷勢嚴重失去半個肝，並因受感染要接受輸血治理，留院8天，胸口留下12吋長的疤痕。<br />\n被告的施襲的原因，是霍根在社交網站facebook向他的女友發「交友邀請」，控方指被告是完全誤解了當中的意思，指霍根只想與他的女友普通聊天，卻遇上幾乎奪命的襲擊。<br />\n法官賀爾（Jonathan Durham Hall）指亨特因一個明顯是單純的facebook接觸而施襲，非常令人震驚，又形容被告懦弱卑劣而且不友善，故判刑7年。法官警告被告如有再犯，將會判囚終身。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190113/large/1547353823_bf90.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190113%2Flarge%2F1547353823_bf90.jpg&h=6349f9ab&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3aa6d283d77c8a7b11697307f2b7b095a77013eb","tid":980936,"uid":191926,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T00:42:41.000Z","msg":"有少少像迪基亞"},{"pid":"a24c047edceda7a12ae3fd4cec0ce8333ccaef62","tid":980936,"uid":107364,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T00:43:26.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2f8fa0f98e461c99a5212007bf7899e6e5ed64d9","tid":980936,"uid":131884,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T00:45:57.000Z","msg":"個平陰<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"119255707635952b2f56558e43b21256c24c9dfd","tid":980936,"uid":201274,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T00:53:18.000Z","msg":"ddg<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"h